Delhi Corona Daily Report: 21 May

#Delhi reported 571 new cases of Covid-19 in the last 24 hours, the State's steepest single-day spike while 375 patients recovered in the same period.

Active cases in the capital stands at 5898.

#COVID19India #Covid_19india #Covid_19 https://t.co/mrdwCgqeTF
